Show VCard 3.0 Contact Photo for sender or Gravatar Icon for Sender

This plugin will show contact picture for message sender.
This will only work with Roundcube 0.6-svn  

Enable the plugin in config/main.inc.php
$rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('show_contactimg');

Set tmp Folder rights to writeable

Author Eric Appelt
Website http://www.php-lexikon.de

Changes:
v0.4 - Fix show picture from another User for the same Contact
v0.3 - add support for Gravatar Images as Fallback
v0.2 - add support for global Addressbook plugin
